Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:22.25,OP中文,,0,0,0,,我们在零重力之中起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:27.97,OP中文,,0,0,0,,飞速旅行到遥远的星际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.65,0:00:35.49,OP中文,,0,0,0,,需要特殊的快递吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:38.05,OP中文,,0,0,0,,只需叫上Malo Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.13,0:00:41.29,OP中文,,0,0,0,,但不是免费的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.05,0:00:48.81,OP中文,,0,0,0,,Malo Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.21,0:00:52.45,OP中文,,0,0,0,,没人能打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.45,0:00:55.13,OP中文,,0,0,0,,Malo Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:57.93,OP中文,,0,0,0,,生活在宇宙中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:22.25,OP英文,,0,0,0,,We can dance in zero G
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:27.97,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Traveling fast far from galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.65,0:00:35.49,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Need a special delivery
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:38.05,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Just call Malo Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.13,0:00:41.29,OP英文,,0,0,0,,But it's not free
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.05,0:00:48.81,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Malo Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.21,0:00:52.45,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Nobody will bring you down
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.45,0:00:55.13,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Malo Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:57.93,OP英文,,0,0,0,,live in space
