Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:09.09,MK标题,,0,0,0,,{\pos(342,312)}{\fad(800,900)}#5                    破冰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:20.39,MK英文,,0,0,0,,3J, here. Welcome to Intergalactic Tracer Radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:23.02,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Tell Cyana, aboard the Starduke,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:25.30,MK英文,,0,0,0,,that her family needs her. It's urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:49.70,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Ah haha! Get ready to pay for another round, Jonas?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.37,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Blistering black hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:54.37,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You got easy with those long arms of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:02:58.72,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Greetings friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:02.12,MK英文,,0,0,0,,This is 3J, king of the Galactic Radio Network.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:04.85,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I have a message for a Starduke crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:07.85,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Cyana, your family needs you. It's urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:10.70,MK英文,,0,0,0,,My family? But you're both right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.10,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Wait till I get my hands on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:36.12,MK英文,,0,0,0,,My princesses. My lovely princesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:36.65,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Cyana?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:38.65,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Cyana?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:41.67,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:45.70,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Your father wouldn't be calling if it weren't serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:46.87,MK英文,,0,0,0,,We'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:15.37,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Your younger sister has come to her senses, princess Edith.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:19.17,MK英文,,0,0,0,,She has decided to return to the palace under our protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:21.95,MK英文,,0,0,0,,{\u1}Buary{\u0}? You've captured {\u1}Buary{\u0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:26.30,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Captured her? Hmm. Do you take me for a pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:30.45,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You must sign if you want to save your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:32.52,MK英文,,0,0,0,,And what remains of your kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:34.02,MK英文,,0,0,0,,What remains of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.35,MK英文,,0,0,0,,If I sign
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:37.35,MK英文,,0,0,0,,the League will consider that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:40.05,MK英文,,0,0,0,,the theft of our ice by your Consortium to be legal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:42.07,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Nothing will stand in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:45.87,MK英文,,0,0,0,,The Consortium's business practices do not include theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:49.12,MK英文,,0,0,0,,With our help, Alba Khair will grow rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:52.75,MK英文,,0,0,0,,We will give you ten percent of our sales revenues on the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.45,MK英文,,0,0,0,,It's out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:57.47,MK英文,,0,0,0,,This world is belonged to our ancestors for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:05:00.92,MK英文,,0,0,0,,In that case your fater will soon be joining his ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:03.70,MK英文,,0,0,0,,No! Don't harm my father and sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:06.77,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I...I will sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:25.87,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd prove to have more business sense than your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:32.90,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Commence operations immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:10.60,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Oh! Edith, my princess. What have they done to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:13.40,MK英文,,0,0,0,,There's no point in imagining the worst, your majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:15.42,MK英文,,0,0,0,,It's possible that she's simply sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:17.27,MK英文,,0,0,0,,If so, all is lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:19.96,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Not all, for princess Buary is still free.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:23.62,MK英文,,0,0,0,,What can she do alone against Yago and his Consortium.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:26.17,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Princess Buary was clever and resourceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:29.92,MK英文,,0,0,0,,She will find her sister wherever in the universe she may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:32.15,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Buary will contacts Cyana?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:34.00,MK英文,,0,0,0,,No, that is not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:36.07,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I disinherited Cyana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:37.50,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Banished her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:40.00,MK英文,,0,0,0,,She will never agree to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:00.22,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Any idea what's going on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:02.05,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Not the faintest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:03.37,MK英文,,0,0,0,,But Jonas is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:06.67,MK英文,,0,0,0,,If my father's decided to swallow his pride and call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.20,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Then it must be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:13.42,MK英文,,0,0,0,,With this diadem,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:16.37,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Edith, my daughter, I hereby pronounce you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:18.42,MK英文,,0,0,0,,crown princess of Alba Khair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:25.40,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Ah, it is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:26.65,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Is it very heavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:29.35,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Less heavy than my new responsibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:30.30,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:31.87,MK英文,,0,0,0,,We'll always be here to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:34.35,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You are mistaken, Cyana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.30,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You will leave Alba Khair
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:39.49,MK英文,,0,0,0,,when you are old enough to marry a prince from a nearby kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:41.82,MK英文,,0,0,0,,That time is fast approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:44.80,MK英文,,0,0,0,,It is your duty as the second princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:47.12,MK英文,,0,0,0,,And what if I don't want to get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.22,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You have no choice in the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:52.57,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I want you to meet my {\u1}Naro Sakatara{\u0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:54.95,MK英文,,0,0,0,,the crown prince of Alba {\u1}Vossler{\u0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:59.45,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Our diplomatic relations with his family are excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.87,MK英文,,0,0,0,,And to make them even more so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:04.80,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You and he are to be married.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:08.90,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I'm not getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:09.27,MK英文,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:11.67,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry Prince. It's nothing personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.85,MK英文,,0,0,0,,But I refuse to be bartered away like an object.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:16.50,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I have other plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:18.45,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:19.95,MK英文,,0,0,0,,What's other plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.35,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I want to be a pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:26.02,MK英文,,0,0,0,,A second princess cannot possibly hope to become a pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:29.65,MK英文,,0,0,0,,It is the duty of a second princess to marry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:31.40,MK英文,,0,0,0,,That is the ancient tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:35.92,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Cyana, if you leave this planet, I will disinherit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:37.05,MK英文,,0,0,0,,My mind is made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:39.92,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I will become a pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:46.52,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Communications are blacked out on Alba Khair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:48.87,MK英文,,0,0,0,,There will be no signals for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:51.42,MK英文,,0,0,0,,But there's nothing worth stealing on my planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:53.42,MK英文,,0,0,0,,No mines no high technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.37,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all in fact, except ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.07,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You're right princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:09:01.07,MK英文,,0,0,0,,That ice contains a fifty percent concentration of ZZU minerals,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:04.47,MK英文,,0,0,0,,which gives you and your kind exceptional physical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:07.80,MK英文,,0,0,0,,All right. If someone were stealing it, what would they do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:10.15,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Sell it to planets outside the League.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:14.00,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Imagine an army of men as strong and as fast as the Khair's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.67,0:09:22.95,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Nice planet, Cyana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:32.20,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Seems to be attracting a lot of tourists.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:34.40,MK英文,,0,0,0,,This traffic must be under surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:35.82,MK英文,,0,0,0,,We will be spotted in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.42,0:09:38.40,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Out of we hide like a pilot vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:56.57,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Great globular clusters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:20.82,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:23.00,MK英文,,0,0,0,,See if I care my word,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:26.20,MK英文,,0,0,0,,was I promised you've been reunited with your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:29.22,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry I gave in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:33.12,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Now you can stay together for a long long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:42.00,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Unauthorized personnel on platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:45.17,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Korrigan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:58.02,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Cor cosmic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:01.17,MK英文,,0,0,0,,This place is colder than the caves of Arctic {\u1}major{\u0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:02.92,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I'm going down to the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.32,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I want to find my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:06.52,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it's wise for you to go along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.07,0:11:09.90,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Malo, if they're in danger, it's up to me to help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:12.30,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.82,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile Jonas and I'll try and create a diversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:16.75,MK英文,,0,0,0,,By bringing down this platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:19.65,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Will we making ourselves useful and having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.25,0:11:21.82,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Well princess, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:37.50,MK英文,,0,0,0,,This leviathan is kept airborne by antigravity turbines.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:38.77,MK英文,,0,0,0,,One on each corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:41.52,MK英文,,0,0,0,,If we blow them, the whole thing comes down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:50.20,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Attention all droid units,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.52,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I want surveillance on the elevators,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:55.55,MK英文,,0,0,0,,and I want the whole platform surged.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:06.35,MK英文,,0,0,0,,No, she is alone and Korrigan's the one I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:13.90,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Malo, Yago and one of his thugs are coming your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:14.85,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Thanks Cyana.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:17.50,MK英文,,0,0,0,,All right, you take care of the turbines
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:18.97,MK英文,,0,0,0,,and I will welcome our visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:35.45,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I don't think that's the best way to do it, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:39.50,MK英文,,0,0,0,,For starters the turbines bound to be armored
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:40.72,MK英文,,0,0,0,,and more importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:43.62,MK英文,,0,0,0,,every droid in 5 parsecs radius will come running.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:48.05,MK英文,,0,0,0,,My name's Jonas, chief mechanic aboard the Starduke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:50.50,MK英文,,0,0,0,,And from the description Cyana had given me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:52.90,MK英文,,0,0,0,,you must be her younger sister {\u1}Buary{\u0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:55.95,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Cyana? Do you...Do you know Cyana?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:56.95,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I sure do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.65,MK英文,,0,0,0,,In fact I came here with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.12,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You mean she's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:01.92,MK英文,,0,0,0,,She's on Alba Khair?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.02,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You hold this will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:12.57,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, even the vulture armored.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:14.57,MK英文,,0,0,0,,How much longer old-timer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:15.97,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Seven minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:19.57,MK英文,,0,0,0,,if I can open this God darn panel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:20.15,MK英文,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:23.72,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I'll have the Starduke at the Northwest sector in seven minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:38.90,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Yago!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:08.95,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Well, how does this thing work?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:11.82,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Very simple. It's a new killer turbine
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:13.60,MK英文,,0,0,0,,delivering an antigravity pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:16.55,MK英文,,0,0,0,,The inner jerk ran with a swirling mass of negatons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:20.55,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Negatons are electrons with an extra negative charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:23.02,MK英文,,0,0,0,,And this is an old proton gun, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:28.42,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Of course and protons are positively charged.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:30.82,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Oh-oh, Cyana was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.72,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Little sister you're a clever girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:35.32,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Now for some nice fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:39.12,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Presents battle authorisation immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:43.77,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Do not move. This is your final warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:46.35,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Hang on little sister. It's showtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:16.25,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Something's gone wrong with the anti-gravity systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:26.72,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Your little stroll is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.50,0:17:38.47,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Cyana?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:43.47,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:26.37,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You old alley cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:28.15,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I'll leave you alone for five minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:29.50,MK英文,,0,0,0,,and I find you with a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:31.87,MK英文,,0,0,0,,That's too old for that stuff kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:34.87,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Too old for ladies and too old for a {\u1}dramatic.{\u0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:36.77,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Now then, how about one for the all?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:37.45,MK英文,,0,0,0,,To begin, let me assure everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:41.15,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Since I am living and a death is not yet on the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:43.55,MK英文,,0,0,0,,The treaty that she signed under duress
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:46.12,MK英文,,0,0,0,,is not legally binding in the eyes of the League.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:50.27,MK英文,,0,0,0,,And so the ice of Alba Khair still belongs to the Khair's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:56.40,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Some time ago I shamefully disinherited Cyana,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:58.40,MK英文,,0,0,0,,my beloved second daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:02.20,MK英文,,0,0,0,,But on this day I am asking for her forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:07.32,MK英文,,0,0,0,,And I am restoring her to her rank and her place among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:14.07,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Cyana, ask me for anything. It shall be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:20.10,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Father, my wish is to remain the mysteries of my destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:25.17,MK英文,,0,0,0,,But I can never find true happiness without your blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:27.12,MK英文,,0,0,0,,This means you are leaving again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:29.45,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Though we've only just been reunited.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:33.40,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I shall never see the stars without thinking of the dangers you face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:36.75,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless I accept your choice
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:40.25,MK英文,,0,0,0,,and I dub you the first pilot princess of Alba Khair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:50.45,MK英文,,0,0,0,,My princesses. My lovely princesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:04.30,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Glad to see you back in good spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:08.07,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, Malo, you can't imagine how it feels to see one's father again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:13.20,MK英文,,0,0,0,,No, you're right. I can't imagine how that feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:14.97,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:16.85,MK英文,,0,0,0,,It's all right princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.62,0:21:20.82,MK英文,,0,0,0,,For the queen of co-pilots, I'll forgive anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.25,0:21:42.15,OP中文,,0,0,0,,我们在零重力之中起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:45.85,OP中文,,0,0,0,,飞速旅行到遥远的星际
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:48.40,OP中文,,0,0,0,,Malo Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:52.23,OP中文,,0,0,0,,没人能打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.43,0:21:54.91,OP中文,,0,0,0,,Malo Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:57.80,OP中文,,0,0,0,,生活在宇宙中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.25,0:21:42.15,OP英文,,0,0,0,,We can dance in zero G{\pos(480,45)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:45.85,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Traveling fast far from galaxy{\pos(480,45)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:48.40,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Malo Korrigan{\pos(480,45)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:52.23,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Nobody will bring you down{\pos(480,45)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.43,0:21:54.91,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Malo Korrigan{\pos(480,45)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:57.80,OP英文,,0,0,0,,live in space{\pos(480,45)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:20.39,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这里是3J 欢迎来到太空牛仔广播
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:23.02,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,告诉星爵号上的Cyana
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:25.30,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,她的家人需要她 这很紧急
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:49.70,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,啊哈 准备好再来一局了吗 Jonas
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.37,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,真像是膨胀的黑洞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:54.37,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,用你那长长的胳膊玩这个游戏实在是太简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:02:58.72,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:02.12,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这里是3J 太空牛仔广播的管理者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:04.85,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我有条给星爵号乘员的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:07.85,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Cyana 你的家人需要你 这是紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:10.70,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我的家人 可你们都在这儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.10,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,等我抓住你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:36.12,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我亲爱的公主们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:36.65,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Cyana
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:38.65,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Cyana
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:41.67,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:45.70,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,只有紧急情况 你父亲才会召唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:46.87,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我们和你一道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:15.37,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你的妹妹回过神来了 Edith公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:19.17,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,她决定在我们的看守下返回宫殿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:21.95,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Buary 你抓住了Buary吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:26.30,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,抓住她 呃 你当我们是海盗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:30.45,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,想要救你的父亲你必须签署这份协议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:32.52,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,同时还能保留你们王国
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:34.02,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,可是这份协议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.35,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,如果我签署了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:37.35,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,星际联盟就会认为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:40.05,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你们财团窃取我们冰资源的行为是合法的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:42.07,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,没人能容忍你这种行为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:45.87,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,财团的商业活动并不包括盗窃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:49.12,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,在我们的帮助下 Alba Khair将会变得富裕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:52.75,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我们会把冰资源的销售所得的十分之一返还给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.45,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这没得谈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:57.47,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,数个世纪以来 我们的祖先一直统治着这个星球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:05:00.92,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,如果这样的话 你的父亲很快就要加入到他祖先的行列了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:03.70,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,不 不要伤害我的父亲和姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:06.77,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我 我会签
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:25.87,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,相比于你父亲 我知道你更有商业头脑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:32.90,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,立刻开始行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:10.60,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 Edith 我的公主 他们会对你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:13.40,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,没必要设想最坏的情况 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:15.42,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,她可能就签署了协议
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:17.27,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,如果这样的话 那一切都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:19.96,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这不完全 Buary公主依然没被控制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:23.62,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,她一个人又怎么能反抗Yago和他的财团
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:26.17,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Buary足智多谋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:29.92,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,她能在宇宙的角落里找到她的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:32.15,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Buary会联系Cyana吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:34.00,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,不 这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:36.07,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我废黜了Cyana
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:37.50,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,赶走了她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:40.00,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,她永远都不愿来帮助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:00.22,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你觉得那儿会发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:02.05,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,并不是不能想象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:03.37,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,不过Jonas说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:06.67,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,如果我父亲决定放下尊严召唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.20,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,那事态一定很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:13.42,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,以国王的名义
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:16.37,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我的女儿 Edith 我特此宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:18.42,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你成为了Alba Khair的女王储
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:25.40,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,啊 这真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:26.65,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这很重吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:29.35,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,比我刚接下的责任要轻一些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:30.30,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:31.87,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我们会帮助你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:34.35,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Cyana 你搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.30,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你将要离开Alba Khair
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:39.49,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,当你年龄达到要求时 你需要嫁给邻国的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:41.82,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这个时候很快就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:44.80,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这是你作为第二公主的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:47.12,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,但如果我不想嫁人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.22,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,在这件事上你无从选择
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:52.57,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我想让你见见Naro Sakatara
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:54.95,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,他是Alba Vossler的王储
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:59.45,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我们和这个家族的外交关系非常密切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.87,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,为了进一步促进这个关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:04.80,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你和他需要结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:08.90,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我不想结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:09.27,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:11.67,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,王子 我很抱歉 我不是针对你个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.85,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,但是我拒绝被当作物品来交易
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:16.50,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我还是另请高明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:18.45,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,容我冒昧地问一句
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:19.95,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你要另请什么高明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.35,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我想成为飞船驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:26.02,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,第二公主绝不能成为一个驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:29.65,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,第二公主的义务就是嫁人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:31.40,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这是古代的传统
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:35.92,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Cyana 如果你要离开这个星球 那我就要废黜你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:37.05,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我去意已决
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:39.92,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我要成为一个驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:46.52,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Alba Khair的通信已经受到管制
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:48.87,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,未来三天都将没有信号
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:51.42,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,但是我的星球上并没有值得窃取的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:53.42,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,没有矿产也没有高科技
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.37,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,实际上除了冰以外没有任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.07,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,公主你说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:09:01.07,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这种冰矿含有50%浓度的ZZU矿物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:04.47,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这种矿物带给你们种族不寻常的肉体能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:07.80,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 如果有人窃取冰矿 他们的目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:10.15,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,把冰矿卖给星际联盟以外的行星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:14.00,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,想象这样一支军队 每个士兵都和Alba Khair人一样强壮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.67,0:09:22.95,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,不错的行星 Cyana
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:32.20,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,看起来像是吸引了很多游客
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:34.40,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这个交通肯定处在监视之下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:35.82,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我们很快就会被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.42,0:09:38.40,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,除非我们藏身于驾驶员的视野盲区
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:56.57,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:20.82,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:23.00,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,看看我是不是遵守承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:26.20,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我之前保证过你能和你父亲团聚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:29.22,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,对不起 我妥协了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:33.12,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,现在你们能永远团聚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:42.00,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,未授权人士出现在平台上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:45.17,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:58.02,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:01.17,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这个地方甚至比北极的洞穴还要冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:02.92,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我去下面的宫殿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.32,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我想找到我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:06.52,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我不认为你一个人去是明智的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.07,0:11:09.90,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Malo 如果他们处在危险当中 那么正应该是我去搭救
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:12.30,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,足够合理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.82,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,与此同时Jonas和我将吸引敌人的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:16.75,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,通过摧毁这个平台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:19.65,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我们能在找乐子的同时让自己变得有用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.25,0:11:21.82,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 公主 祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:37.50,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这个平台由反重力涡轮提供悬浮的动力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:38.77,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,每个角上都有一台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:41.52,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,如果我们炸毁它们 整个平台都会坠毁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:50.20,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,所有机器人注意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.52,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我希望有人在电梯上监视
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:55.55,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,同时增派更多人手到平台上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:06.35,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,不必去追 她只是一个人 Korrigan才是我想找的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:13.90,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Malo Yago和他的一个伙计正赶往你们那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:14.85,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Cyana 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:17.50,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 你来处置那些涡轮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:18.97,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,而我来欢迎访客
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:35.45,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我不认为这是解决问题的最好方式 小姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:39.50,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,首先 这些涡轮被装甲保护着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:40.72,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,而且更重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:43.62,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,四周的机器人追兵很快就会过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:48.05,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我叫Jonas 星爵号上的首席机械师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:50.50,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,通过Cyana给我的描述来看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:52.90,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你应该是她的妹妹Buary
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:55.95,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Cyana 你 你知道Cyana吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:56.95,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.65,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,事实上 我和她一块过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.12,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你的意思是她也在这儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:01.92,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,在Alba Khair吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.02,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你就保持着这个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:12.57,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 就连这东西都趁人之危 被保护起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:14.57,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,老伙计你还要多久
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:15.97,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,7分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:19.57,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,如果我能打开这个顽固的控制面板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:20.15,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:23.72,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,7分钟内 我会把星爵号开到西北角
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:38.90,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Yago
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:08.95,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,诶 这东西是怎么工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:11.82,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,图森破 这是个很厉害的新型涡轮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:13.60,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,发送出反重力脉冲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:16.55,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,内部的涡轮搅动着大量电子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:20.55,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,电子带负电荷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:23.02,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,而这不就是把老式质子枪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:28.42,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,当然啦 质子是带正电荷的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:30.82,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,啊哦 Cyana说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.72,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,小妹妹你真聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:35.32,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,现在是烟火时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:39.12,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:43.77,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,不许动 这是最终的警告
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:46.35,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,稳住咯小妹妹 开始咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:16.25,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,反重力系统出了点问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:26.72,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,没时间给你四处闲逛了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.50,0:17:38.47,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Cyana
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:43.47,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:26.37,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你这条野猫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:28.15,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我离开你才只有5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:29.50,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,就发现你带了个妹子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:31.87,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这个笑话太老套了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:34.87,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,对女士们太老套 对我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:36.77,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,现在 一发入魂如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:37.45,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,首先 让我给各位保证
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:41.15,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,因为我还活着而且也没有在王位上死去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:43.55,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Edith在胁迫之下签署的协议
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:46.12,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,在星际联盟看来并不具有法律效应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:50.27,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,所以Alba Khair上的冰矿依旧属于大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:56.40,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,不久之前我可耻地废黜了Cyana
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:58.40,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我亲爱的二女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:02.20,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,但是今天我请求她的怜悯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:07.32,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,并且恢复她在我们中的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:14.07,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Cyana 向我请求任何补偿 这是应属于你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:20.10,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,爸爸 我的心愿是不告诉你我的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:25.17,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,但是我的幸福也来源自你的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:27.12,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这意味着你又要离开我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:29.45,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,尽管我们刚刚才团聚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:33.40,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我一看到星空就会想起你面临的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:36.75,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,尽管如此 我同意你的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:40.25,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,并且我承认你作为Alba Khair的第一个驾驶员公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:50.45,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我亲爱的公主们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:04.30,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,很高兴看到你容光焕发地回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:08.07,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 Malo 你不能想象和父亲团聚的那种感受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:13.20,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你说的没错 我是没法想象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:14.97,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:16.85,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,没关系 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.62,0:21:20.82,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,对于副驾驶的女王而言 我会原谅一切的
